---
import SocialButtons from "./ui/SocialButtons.astro";
---

<div class="w-full pt-20 flex items-center justify-center bg-[#202127]">
  <div class="md:w-2/3 w-full px-4 text-white flex flex-col">
    <div class="w-full text-6xl font-bold">
      <h1 class="w-full md:w-2/3">Tu crecimiento es nuestra misión.</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="flex mt-8 flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between items-center">
      <p class="w-full md:w-2/3 text-gray-400">
        Nos dedicamos a hacer realidad tus objetivos. Con soluciones
        personalizadas y un enfoque comprometido, trabajamos para que tu negocio
        no solo crezca, sino que prospere.
      </p>
      <div class="w-fit md:pt-0">
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/5493865415222"
          class="cta w-full mt-8 bg-yellow-400 text-black cursor-pointer"
        >
          +54 9 3865 41-5222
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col text-center justify-center">
      <div class="flex mt-24 mb-12 flex-row justify-between items-center">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="logo-navbar text-3xl hover:scale-110 transition-transform transform"
        >
          TRICODE
        </a>
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="hidden md:block cursor-pointer text-gray-600 hover:text-white uppercase"
          >About</a
        >
        <a
          href="/services"
          class="hidden md:block cursor-pointer text-gray-600 hover:text-white uppercase"
          >Services</a
        >
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="hidden md:block cursor-pointer text-gray-600 hover:text-white uppercase"
          >Contact</a
        >
        <div class="flex flex-row space-x-8 items-center justify-between">
          <SocialButtons />
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr class="border-gray-600" />
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
        <p class="text-center mt-12 text-gray-500 text-lg">
          Dev.tricode@gmail.com
        </p>
        <p class="text-center pb-6 text-gray-600">
          Copyright © 2024 <b>Tricode.</b>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .logo-navbar {
      font-family: "Eras";
    }
    .cta {
      display: flex;
      padding: 11px 33px;
      transform: skewX(-15deg);
      border: none;
      transition: 1;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</div>
